@Node About "DLManager About"
@{b}@{u}DLManager About@{ub}@{uu}

DLManager creates files that will contain email addresses and send mails
to those addresses in that file. So, you can send each person the
same email just by selecting the file name and writing the email!

I can be reached at either of the following ways for any questions
comments/bug reports etc...

   @{i}Internet: @{ui}

       EMail: tbouchar@ptialaska.net
	 WWW: http://www.ptialaska.net/~tbouchar
	News: alt.sys.amiga.thor @{b}Not Recommended!! @{ub}
Mailing List: thor-ml@thule.no
	      thor-dev@thule.no
@EndNode

